metadata.name: salsazar - the Pain's Prelate
metadata.description:
Thou who rips the flesh and pierces the vein:
pleasure to meet you, I am the Prelate of Pain.

Do not be fooled by my bloody condition
winning suffering is my sole mission.

The cuts, nails and my face stretched on the staff
barely tickle me, actually they make me laugh!

Enough about me... Sorry to see that cut on your arm
would you like me to mend it and stop all the harm?

I use magic and medicine to win over fear and death
so that you can live in peace till your very last breath.
.
